SIZE=(16,67), ORIENT=(02,07)
WINDOW BOX
EASEL ON


            Primary Account Related Balance Option - Help

    Indicates whether to include the primary account in related
    account balance requirements.  Valid entries are:

      N  Do not include the primary account in the related
         account requirements.
      Y  Include the primary account in the related account
         requirements.  Uses the balance requirements from
         Related Balance Category Codes 1 and 2 on MICM Record
         7102 (Product Definition).
                                                                _
    F12=Cancel                                            M01088S

EASEL OFF
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
FIELD=PFKEY,    PIC='X(01)', ATTR=(DISPLAY,HIDDEN)
LABEL=(LABEL,IMPORTANT)
